  "title": "ACCOUNTS ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in daily accounting operations (AR/AP)</p></li><li><p>Prepare invoices, payments, and receipts</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper accounting records and filing</p></li><li><p>Perform data entry into accounting systems</p></li><li><p>Assist with monthly closing and reports</p></li><li><p>Support audits and ad-hoc finance tasks</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Certificate in Accounting / Finance or related field</p></li><li><p>At least 1 year of relevant working experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of accounting principles</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Excel; accounting software experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Careful, organized, and responsible</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li></ul>",
